      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no actual rest left for me. even sleeping feels like another chore, another thing I'm failing at. everything is just... constant. like, even if i quit the program, i'll still be this person who failed. is it even worth trying to fix things when the core of everything is just broken? it feels like the only way to actually get some peace is to just stop everything. completely.",
